{"TopicId":211554,"ForumId":112,"TopicTitle":"Add button \u0026quot;Exit to Windows\u0026quot;","CreatedByName":"Vortygont","CreatedById":223549,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-17T20:16:57Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Vortygont","CreatedById":223549,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-17T20:16:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the game now in the pause menu there is only a button to \u0022Exit to the menu\u0022, but in most other games there is also a button to \u0022Exit to Windos\u0022. This is very important because it saves people time so they do not have to load the main menu before closing the game\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-17T20:35:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlt\u002BF4\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bej Kerman","CreatedById":182413,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-17T21:11:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224220857\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211554\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221673987730\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n33 minutes ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlt\u002BF4\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlt-F4 works fine but it\u0027d be nice to have a button that lets us exit anywhere\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Ewithout\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0losing progress and also potentially breaking things if done during an autosave.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nazalassa","CreatedById":217956,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-18T18:58:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022Exit to OS\u0022 is better (not everybody uses Windows)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"darthgently","CreatedById":204885,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-18T19:15:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224221227\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211554\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221674068315\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022217956\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nazalassa\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 minutes ago, Nazalassa said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022Exit to OS\u0022 is better (not everybody uses Windows)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy \u0022exit to os\u0022 is a bash script:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nkill -TERM \u0060pgrep KSP\u0060; sleep 10; kill -KILL \u0060pgrep KSP\u0060\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*Save First*\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-01-18T19:16:44Z\u0022 title=\u002201/18/2023 07:16  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 18, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by darthgently\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-19T01:46:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224220845\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022211554\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221673986617\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022223549\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vortygont\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 1/17/2023 at 3:16 PM, Vortygont said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the game now in the pause menu there is only a button to \u0022Exit to the menu\u0022, but in most other games there is also a button to \u0022Exit to Windos\u0022. This is very important because it saves people time so they do not have to load the main menu before closing the game\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nQuickExit\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Skorj","CreatedById":201273,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-19T07:15:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022Exit to Desktop\u0022 is the usual wording.\u00A0 Should update the persistent save and exit, vs Alt-F4 which should exit cleanly but not save.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}